OL,3,CThames Water warns over 44% bill hike
OL,4,Cunder new business plans
OL,6,FTroubled Thames Water has put forward
OL,7,Fnew plans to boost spending and
OL,8,Finvestment in its network, but warned
OL,9,Fthis could see customer bills surge by
OL,10,F44%.
OL,12,FThe group, which is battling to
OL,13,Fsurvive amid a funding crisis, has
OL,14,Fproposed increasing spending by #1.1
OL,15,Fbillion and revealed another potential
OL,16,F#1.9 billion investment in its network
OL,17,Fas part of new business plans to
OL,18,Fregulator Ofwat.
