OL,3,CThames Water warns over 44% bill hike
OL,4,Cunder new business plans
OL,6,FThe firm ` Britain's biggest water
OL,7,Ffirm, with 16 million customers in
OL,8,FLondon and the Thames Valley region `
OL,9,Fsaid its new business plan for the
OL,10,Ffive years to 2030 would see spending
OL,11,Frise to #19.8 billion, with the extra
OL,12,Fbeing used for environmental projects.
OL,14,FBut it added that the possible extra
OL,15,F#1.9 billion investment in its network
OL,16,Fwould see average customer bills rise
OL,17,Fby another #19 over the five years `
OL,18,Fon top of the 40% hike already
OL,19,Fpencilled.
