OL,3,CThames Water warns over 44% bill hike
OL,4,Cunder new business plans
OL,6,FIf Ofwat were to give the full plans
OL,7,Fthe go ahead, this would see customer
OL,8,Fbills rise to #627 a year by 2030.
OL,10,FChris Weston, chief executive of
OL,11,FThames Water, said: "Our business plan
OL,12,Ffocuses on our customers' priorities.
OL,14,F"As part of the usual ongoing
OL,15,Fdiscussions relating to (the business
OL,16,Fplan), we've now updated it to deliver
OL,17,Fmore projects that will benefit the
OL,18,Fenvironment.
OL,20,F"We will continue to discuss this with
OL,21,Four regulators and stakeholders."
