OL,3,CThames Water warns over 44% bill hike
OL,4,Cunder new business plans
OL,6,FThames Water has had to rethink its
OL,7,Fbusiness plan in a bid to stave off
OL,8,Fcollapse as it crumbles under the
OL,9,Fweight of #15 billion of debt.
OL,11,FIts investors have refused to pump in
OL,12,Fthe cash needed to plug a funding gap
OL,13,Fand reports suggest the Government is
OL,14,Fworking on plans to effectively
OL,15,Fnationalise the water giant.
